                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Achievements Section -->
    <section class="section achievements-section bg-surface">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Key Achievements</h2>
        <div class="achievements-grid">
          <div class="achievement-card card">
            <div class="achievement-icon">üåç</div>
            <h3>Global Impact</h3>
            <p>
              Managed worldwide IBM application serving users across multiple
              countries and billing systems
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="achievement-card card">
            <div class="achievement-icon">üë•</div>
            <h3>Team Leadership</h3>
            <p>
              Led cross-functional teams of 30+ members delivering enterprise
              solutions
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="achievement-card card">
            <div class="achievement-icon">üéì</div>
            <h3>Training Excellence</h3>
            <p>
              Awarded "Best Trainer of Aptech Qatar" and managed team of 7
              certified trainers
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="achievement-card card">
            <div class="achievement-icon">üìä</div>
            <h3>Data-Driven</h3>
            <p>
              Leveraged Python, Pandas, and PostgreSQL for comprehensive
              analytics and KPI tracking
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="achievement-card card">
            <div class="achievement-icon">üèÜ</div>
